）</li>	<li>莱斯-<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/南开大学" target="_blank">南开大学</a>可持续发展研究（China Nankai University Partnership for Sustainable Development）*(4)</li></ul><p><strong>研究领域</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:37.94%">研究领域名称</td>			<td style="width:62.06%">			<p>研究领域英文名</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:37.94%">			<p>环境工程</p>			</td>			<td style="width:62.06%">			<p>Environmental engineering</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:37.94%">			<p>水文与水资源工程</p>			</td>			<td style="width:62.06%">			<p>Hydrology and water resources</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:37.94%">			<p>结构工程与<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/机械工程" target="_blank">机械工程</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:62.06%">			<p>Structural engineering and mechanics</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:37.94%">			<p>城市基础设施建设与管理</p>			</td>			<td style="width:62.06%">			<p>Urban infrastructure and management</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:37.94%">			<p>环境应用与纳米技术及影响</p>			</td>			<td style="width:62.06%">			<p>Environmental applications and implications of nanotechnology</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:37.94%">			<p>环境生物技术与生物修复</p>			</td>			<td style="width:62.06%">			<p>Environmental biotechnology and bioremediation</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:37.94%">			<p>城市空气质量与大气化学</p>			</td>			<td style="width:62.06%">			<p>Urban air quality and atmospheric chemistry</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:37.94%">			<p>水资源、洪水预报及减灾</p>			</td>			<td style="width:62.06%">			<p>Water resources, flood prediction and disaster mitigation</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:37.94%">			<p>水净化与废水回用先进技术</p>			</td>			<td style="width:62.06%">			<p>Advanced technologies for water purification and waste water reuse</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:37.94%">			<p>水生与胶体化学</p>			</td>			<td style="width:62.06%">			<p>Aquatic and colloid chemistry</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style